    <values>
        <field>Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">One or more users are assigned to a delegated administration group that grants the ability to manage other users within a defined scope.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Impact__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Delegated admins with broad group scope can indirectly escalate privileges by assigning high-privilege permission sets to themselves or others within their permitted scope.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Review all delegated administration groups. Verify each group has the minimum necessary scope. Ensure delegated admins cannot assign permission sets that include Modify All Data or API Enabled.</value>
